WEBVTT

00:00:01.038 --> 00:00:06.788
In 2018, two Black men
went to a Starbucks

00:00:06.829 --> 00:00:08.746
to wait for a business associate.

00:00:09.413 --> 00:00:11.413
But when they asked to use the bathroom,

00:00:11.454 --> 00:00:13.621
the manager ordered them to leave.

00:00:14.329 --> 00:00:15.829
They refused.

00:00:15.871 --> 00:00:17.288
He called the police,

00:00:17.329 --> 00:00:18.954
and the video went viral.

00:00:19.871 --> 00:00:22.996
Amidst an avalanche of bad publicity,

00:00:23.413 --> 00:00:26.496
Starbucks closed all stores
across the country

00:00:26.538 --> 00:00:29.454
for four hours of diversity training.